              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A carbon catcher situated in direct view of the",
                "239PuO2 deposit was used to collect the 238Pu recoiling",
                "nuclei. The collection efficiency was determined by",
                "238U(n,2n)237U reaction measurements."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ASPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
